== 季节总览 ==
[[File:Agnes_1972_rainfall.gif|thumb]]

1972年大西洋飓风季于1972年6月1日正式开始<ref name="blm" />，虽然形成的热带气旋总数有19个，但只有其中7个达到热带风暴强度<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | archivedate = 2016-04-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160411090349/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-021716.txt | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-021716.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-02-17 | accessdate = 2016-04-26 | format = [[文本文档|TXT]] }}</ref>，低于1950至2000年间每季9.6场风暴获得命名的平均值<ref name="gray2014">{{cite report | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304025541/http://tropical.atmos.colostate.edu/forecasts/2014/apr2014/apr2014.pdf | url = http://tropical.atmos.colostate.edu/forecasts/2014/apr2014/apr2014.pdf | title = Extended Range Forecast of Atlantic Seasonal Hurricane Activity and U.S. Landfall Strike Probability for 2014 | author1 = Philip J. Klotzbach | author2 = William M. Gray | date = 2014-04-10 | publisher = Colorado State University | page = 2 | accessdate = 2016-04-26 | location = Fort Collins, Colorado | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。全部7场热带或亚热带风暴中只有3场成为飓风<ref name="HURDAT" />，同样低于往年均值<ref name="gray2014" />。全季没有形成[[热带气旋分级|大型飓风]]，即没有风暴达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]中的三级飓风标准<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref name="gray2014"/>。总体而言，1972年大西洋飓风季的活跃程度很低，期间出现的[[东风波|东风波]]数量虽然同[[1971年大西洋飓风季|上一季]]接近，但在[[厄尔尼诺现象|厄尔尼诺现象]]的影响下，东大西洋的[[海面温度|上层水温]]偏低，[[风切变|垂直风切变]]也比较多，共同导致这种低迷情况出现<ref name="mwr" />。本季共有两场飓风和一场亚热带风暴[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，共夺走137条人命，经济损失超过21亿美元<ref name="mwr" /><ref name="tpbp">{{cite news | newspaper = The Palm Beach Post | date = 1972-05-29 | title = Four Drown in Area Mishaps}}</ref><ref name="ncdc">{{cite journal |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |work=National Climatic Data Center |title=Storm Data May 1972 |volume=14 |number=5 |accessdate=2015-07-07 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-6BB8BD2B-84FD-47A9-B5E6-84825F48FD77.pdf |format=PDF |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707220017/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-6BB8BD2B-84FD-47A9-B5E6-84825F48FD77.pdf |archivedate=2015-07-07 |journal= }}</ref><ref name="blake" /><ref name="HAW2">{{cite report | accessdate = 2016-04-26 | location = Miami, Florida | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/outreach/history/#agnes | title = Hurricane History | year = 2008 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-04-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160418090931/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/outreach/history/#agnes | date =  }}</ref><ref name="meteo">{{cite report | url = http://www.meteo.org/archives/hist06.htm | title = Page d'histoire - Juin | publisher = La Météo au Quotidien | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307073414/http://meteo.org/archives/hist06.htm | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-04-26 | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | date =  }}</ref>。亚热带风暴德尔塔是本季最后一场风暴，于11月7日转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]<ref name="HURDAT" />，这时离飓风季于11月30日正式结束还有23天<ref name="blm" />。

飓风季的热带天气活动于5月拉开帷幕，[[1972年亚热带风暴阿尔法|亚热带风暴阿尔法]]在5月下旬发展形成。6月共生成3个热带气旋，其中包括飓风艾格尼丝和两个热带低气压。7月也形成3个热带天气系统，但都没达到热带风暴强度。8月是本季最繁忙的月份，共形成5个热带气旋，其中3个只达到热带低气压强度，另外两个分别是飓风贝蒂和[[1972年热带风暴卡丽|热带风暴卡丽]]。9月的热带天气活跃度略有回落，形成飓风唐恩、亚热带风暴查理和两个热带低气压。10月也有3个热带低气压形成。11月形成的风暴只有亚热带风暴德尔玛，于1日成形，7日消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />

本季的活跃程度也通过累积[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]的低迷反映出来，只有36，远低于1981至2010年间的中位数92<ref name="gray2014" />，是[[1962年大西洋飓风季|1962年]]后最低的1年<ref name="ACE" />。大致来说，气旋能量指数通过对飓风的强度和持续时间来计算，强度越高，持续时间越长的风暴，其指数也相应越高。只有在热带系统风速达到或超过每小时63公里（34[[节_(单位)|节]]）或热带风暴强度时才会对这一指数进行计算，并纳入全面的气象公告中。通常情况下，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]会在飓风季结束后重新检视相应数据，做出适当调整。<ref name="ACE">{{cite report | work = Hurricane Research Division; Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-02 | title = Atlantic basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | accessdate = 2016-04-26 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304051842/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | location = Miami, Florida }}</ref>

