5月23日，[[南卡罗莱纳州|南]]、[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]东南方向海域的冷芯[[低气压|低气压区]]发展出[[亚热带气旋|亚热带低气压]]。系统起初向东北方向移动，但5月26日又因有[[高压脊|高压脊]]形成而突然大幅转向南下。当天下午，系统强化成亚热带风暴阿尔法，并开始朝[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]海岸逼近。达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时110公里的最高强度后，气旋开始减弱。5月27日晚，风暴以风力时速75公里强度从乔治亚州[[格林县_(乔治亚州)_(1777年)|格林县]]县城[[布伦瑞克_(乔治亚州)|布伦瑞克]]（{{lang|en|Brunswick}}）附近登陆。阿尔法接下来减弱成热带低气压，并于5月29日进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]东北部后消散。<ref>{{cite report | author = Robert Dickson | year = 1972 | title = Weather and Circulation of May 1972 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2015-12-29 | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/100/mwr-100-08-0648.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120604002000/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/100/mwr-100-08-0648.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-06-04 | format = PDF | date =  }}</ref><ref name="mwr" />

佛罗里达州有两人因风暴引起的恶劣海况溺毙，[[杰克逊维尔_(佛罗里达州)|杰克逊维尔]][[梅波特海军基地|梅波特海军基地]]的一座港口被迫暂停开挖加深工作<ref name="tpbp" /><ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Tuscaloosa News | date = 1972-05-28 | title = Cyclone Serves Notice of Hurricane Season | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | url = https://news.google.co.uk/newspapers?id=1WI0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=L5wEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4138,4676389&dq=storm+1972+georgia+may&hl=en | location = Miami, Florida | archive-date = 2020-12-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201209030640/https://news.google.co.uk/newspapers?id=1WI0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=L5wEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4138%2C4676389&dq=storm+1972+georgia+may&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。乔治亚州沿海潮汐比正常水平高0.61至0.91米，引发一定程度的洪灾和海滩侵蚀<ref name="ncdc" /><ref>{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Weather Service Office Savannah, Georgia | date = 1972-05-28 | title = Severe Weather Statement | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | archivedate = 2015-07-08 | deadurl = no | format = [[JPEG|JPG]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150708190723/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/LOCAL/SAV280025Z.JPG | location = Savannah, Georgia | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/LOCAL/SAV280025Z.JPG }}</ref>。[[圣西蒙斯_(乔治亚州)|圣西蒙斯岛]]（{{lang|en|Saint Simons Island}}）的阵风时速有93公里<ref>{{cite report | author = Paul J. Hebert | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 1972-05-28 | title = Bulletin Eight | accessdate = 2015-12-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150708181920/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB280200Z.JPG | archivedate = 2015-07-08 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0175-jpg/1972/atlantic/ST%20ALPHA/PUBLIC/PUB280200Z.JPG }}</ref>。大风刮倒部分树木，还令多条输电线缆中断，乔治亚州东部部分居民家中停电。该州所受破坏程度较轻，但范围甚广，估计损失数额超过5万美元。<ref name="ncdc" />此外，南卡罗莱纳州到佛罗里达州南部都出现中等程度降水<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/dawn1972.html | title = Subtropical Storm Alpha – May 23-29, 1972 | author = David M. Roth | date = 2007-10-26 | work = Weather Prediction Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | location = College Park, Maryland | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201350/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/dawn1972.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。阿尔法是历史上第一个获命名的亚热带风暴<ref name="mwr" />。
