6月14日，[[极锋|极锋]]和[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]上空的上层[[低压槽|低压槽]]共同影响，催生出热带低气压。6月15日，气旋进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西部，到次日时已强化成热带风暴并获名“艾格尼丝”（{{lang|en|Agnes}}）。风暴蜿蜒北上，于6月17日掠过古巴西部。气旋继续增强，于6月18日升级成飓风。之后一天里艾格尼丝的强度波动很小，然后于6月19日从佛罗里达州[[巴拿马城_(佛罗里达州)|巴拿马城]]附近登陆。飓风上岸后迅速减弱，进入乔治亚州时已降级成热带低气压。接下来，风暴的减弱速度放缓，并经乔治亚州进入南卡罗莱纳州上空。6月21日，艾格尼丝在北卡罗莱纳州东部上空因受[[斜压|斜压活动]]影响而再度增强，达到热带风暴标准。次日清晨，气旋进入大西洋，之后又回转向西北方向移动，以强烈热带风暴标准从[[纽约|纽约]]附近登陆。6月23日，艾格尼丝快速同不含热带特征的低气压天气系统合并。<ref name="mwr" />

古巴西部降下暴雨并引发洪灾，有97套房屋被毁，个别城镇同外界的交通中断，还有低洼地区的农作物被淹<ref name="RE">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = Reading Eagle | date = 1972-06-18 | title = Agnes Ranked As Hurricane | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | location = Miami, Florida | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5I0hAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DpoFAAAAIBAJ&pg=5675,4976346&dq=hurricane+agnes+cuba&hl=en | archive-date = 2022-04-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220413064315/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5I0hAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DpoFAAAAIBAJ&pg=5675%2C4976346&dq=hurricane+agnes+cuba&hl=en }}</ref>，该国共有7人丧生<ref name="HAW2" />。艾格尼丝还催生出大量[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，仅确认的就有26场，其中24场发生在佛罗里达州，两场在乔治亚州。单这些龙卷风就造成价值超过450万美元的破坏，还夺走6条人命。<ref name="ncdc2">{{cite journal |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |work=National Climatic Data Center |title=Storm Data June 1972 |volume=14 |number=6 |accessdate=2015-07-08 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-51688412-A948-4A46-9371-428D1B7B7E85.pdf |format=PDF |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708024237/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-51688412-A948-4A46-9371-428D1B7B7E85.pdf |archivedate=2015-07-08 |location=Asheville, North Carolina |journal= }}</ref>佛罗里达州至少有2082幢建筑不是被毁便是严重受损，另有约1355套住宅受到轻度破坏<ref name="table2">{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070317/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0183-jpg/1972/atlantic/agnes/postevent/damageanddeaths.01.jpg | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 1972 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0183-jpg/1972/atlantic/agnes/postevent/damageanddeaths.01.jpg | title = Impact Of Hurricane Agnes On Property | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | date =  }}</ref>。虽然气旋登陆时尚达飓风标准，但并没有任何地点测得该强度狂风。异常高涨的潮水引起大范围破坏，并以[[阿巴拉契科拉_(佛罗里达州)|阿巴拉契科拉]]到[[锡达礁_(佛罗里达州)|锡达礁]]间区域情况严重<ref name="mwr" />。佛罗里达州共有9人因艾格尼丝丧生，经济损失约为4000万美元<ref name="MCD">{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304214355/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0183-jpg/1972/atlantic/agnes/postevent/report_ashville12.jpg | title = Narrative Summary for Monthly Climatological Data - Florida | date = 1972-07-12 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Climatic Data Center | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | location = Asheville, North Carolina | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0183-jpg/1972/atlantic/agnes/postevent/report_ashville12.jpg }}</ref>。[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]、[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]、乔治亚州、[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]]、南卡罗莱纳州、[[田纳西州|田纳西州]]以及[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]地区都受到气旋影响，但总体程度很轻<ref name="ncdc2" />。但据报导，特拉华州和乔治亚州分别有1人和3人因此遇难<ref name="mwr" />。

[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]是受这场风暴影响最严重的地区，其中大部分破坏都是由严重洪灾引起<ref name="mwr" />。全州以[[斯古吉尔县|斯古吉尔县]]降雨量最高，达460毫米<ref name="rainfall">{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230053/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/agnes1972.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/agnes1972.html | title = Hurricane Agnes - June 14–25, 1972 | author = David M. Roth | date = 2006-09-30 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = Weather Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | location = Camp Springs, Maryland }}</ref>，导致包括[[特拉华河|特拉华河]]、[[萨斯奎哈纳河|萨斯奎哈纳河]]、[[朱尼亚塔河|朱尼亚塔河]]（{{lang|en|Juniata River}}）、[[拉克万纳河|拉克万纳河]]（{{lang|en|Lackawanna River}}）和[[沙士克哈纳河西部支流|沙士克哈纳河西部支流]]（{{lang|en|West Branch Susquehanna River}}）在内的多条河流和溪流浪头高度创下新纪录<ref name="usgs">{{cite report | url = http://pubs.usgs.gov/pp/0924/report.pdf | title = Hurricane Agnes Rainfall and Floods, June-July 1972 | author1 = J. F. Bailey | author2 = J. L. Patterson | date = 1975 | work = [[美国地质调查局|United States Geological Survey]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305012123/http://pubs.usgs.gov/pp/0924/report.pdf | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | location = Reston, Virginia | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。面对洪灾威胁，有十万余人被迫离开家园<ref name="mh0624p20-a">{{cite news | agency = United Press International | newspaper = Miami Herald | date = 1972-06-24 | title = Flood Situation State by State | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193421/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0183-jpg/1972/atlantic/agnes/news/mh0624p20-a.jpg | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | location = Miami, Florida | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0183-jpg/1972/atlantic/agnes/news/mh0624p20-a.jpg | deadurl = no | format = JPG }}</ref>。全州共有超过3000户商铺和6万8000套民房被毁，至少22万人流离失所<ref name="TTL">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160428010030/http://timesleader.com/archive/265255/news-flood_of_memories_06-21-2009-html | url = http://timesleader.com/archive/265255/news-flood_of_memories_06-21-2009-html | title = Agnes now a flood of memories | author = Bill O'Boyle | date = 2015-06-20 | newspaper = The Times Leader | accessdate = 2016-04-28 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-04-28 }}</ref>。截至2015年，艾格尼丝仍然是宾夕法尼亚州历史上造成破坏最严重的自然灾害<ref>{{cite news | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/2002/6-20-agnes-revisited.htm | title = Hurricane Agnes still ranks as Pa.'s worst disaster | date = 2002-06-20 | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = USA Today | accessdate = 2016-04-28 | location = [[哈里斯堡|Harrisburg]], [[宾夕法尼亚州|Pennsylvania]] | archivedate = 2015-09-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924092303/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/2002/6-20-agnes-revisited.htm | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[纽约州|纽约州]]也受到风暴重创，包括[[杰纳西河|杰纳西河]]（{{lang|en|Genesee River}}）、[[阿勒格尼河|阿勒格尼河]]（{{lang|en|Allegheny River}}）、[[希芒河|希芒河]]（{{lang|en|Chemung River}}）、萨斯奎哈纳河及[[泰奥加河|泰奥加河]]在内的许多河流浪头高度刷新原有纪录<ref name="usgs" />。[[科宁_(纽约州)|科宁]]、[[埃尔迈拉_(纽约州)|埃尔迈拉]]和[[奥利安|奥利安]]，以及[[纽约州南部|该州南部]]的许多城镇都爆发重大洪灾<ref name="ncdc2" />。纽约全州共有32万8232户民宅和628幢其它类型建筑受损，1547家小型企业遭到严重破坏或彻底被毁<ref name="table2" />。加拿大有一套移动房屋被推翻，导致两人遇难<ref name="meteo" />。飓风艾格尼丝在美国和加拿大一共夺走131条人命，经济损失超过21亿美元<ref name="blake" /><ref name="HAW2" /><ref name="meteo" />。

